{"tid":1680532,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港空氣咁毒 你唔係唔帶口罩下話？","createTime":"2019-10-29T01:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T01:42:01.000Z","uid":248105,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"52163182a3fff8a4adcf5486e44c2149c87a4958","tid":1680532,"uid":248105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T01:24:58.000Z","msg":"先唔講蒙唔蒙蒙面法<br />\n你老味旺角前一晚閪冧TG放題加狗嫂車噴毒水<br />\n第二朝番工經過 Diu左出黎<br />\n我隔閪住個口罩都嗅撚到嗰陣除<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係隔閪住都嗅到！！！！<br />\n香港人唔係最怕死咩<br />\n嗅毒氣就冇野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩你地唔該帶番個口罩出街<br />\n唔洗屌我隔口罩都嗅到 咁帶黎做咩<br />\n咁港共政府唔聽民意覺得冇用你就唔屌呀？<br />\n只少帶住口罩出街 話比人聽<br />\n比TG洗禮過啲地方空氣係好毒<br />\n最好就人人帶口罩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩推推我"},{"pid":"91afcf717888d6003cfb7fb521ffb7618bd7f277","tid":1680532,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T01:25:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Mfv693.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Mfv693.jpg&h=975a7fc9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0e35d9106aac323ffdb7405d4f613a4bc353b918","tid":1680532,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T01:25:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLdavJJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLdavJJ.gif&h=943b7306&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd1d7ff18339e3050b60877411f74d3201e1e669","tid":1680532,"uid":178066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e35d9106aac323ffdb7405d4f613a4bc353b918","tid":1680532,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T01:25:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLdavJJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum